.kt-grid.kt-grid--ver.kt-grid--root
  #kt_login.kt-grid.kt-grid--hor.kt-grid--root.kt-login.kt-login--v1
    .kt-grid__item.kt-grid__item--fluid.kt-grid.kt-grid--desktop.kt-grid--ver-desktop.kt-grid--hor-tablet-and-mobile
      // BEGIN:: Aside
      .kt-grid__item.kt-grid__item--order-tablet-and-mobile-2.kt-grid.kt-grid--hor.kt-login__aside(style='background-image: url(./assets/media//bg/bg-4.jpg);')
        .kt-grid__item
          a.kt-login__logo(href='/')
            img(width='40%' height='100%' src='./assets/media/logos/logo-4.png')
        .kt-grid__item.kt-grid__item--fluid.kt-grid.kt-grid--ver
          .kt-grid__item.kt-grid__item--middle
            h3.kt-login__title Nie narzekaj, że masz pod górę, gdy zmierzasz na szczyt.
            h4.kt-login__subtitle
              | Myślenie to najcięższa praca z możliwych i pewnie dlatego tak niewielu ją podejmuje.
        .kt-grid__item
          .kt-login__info
            .kt-login__copyright
